00:34:01,563 --> 00:34:03,773
WOMAN: (IN CANTONESE)
This is 33.

479
00:34:03,857 --> 00:34:06,151
WOMAN 2: (IN ENGLISH) Grandma Ming,
you remember last time?

480
00:34:06,234 --> 00:34:08,778
- We wrote it down on a paper.
- (WHIRRING)

481
00:34:08,862 --> 00:34:12,157
