493
00:34:44,189 --> 00:34:45,398
(SIGHS)

494
00:34:45,482 --> 00:34:47,525
Go get me some tea.

495
00:34:50,069 --> 00:34:51,696
You want Oolong or Jasmine?

496
00:34:52,654 --> 00:34:53,698
Whatever.

497
00:34:56,034 --> 00:34:57,869
(BELL TINKLING)

498
00:34:58,787 --> 00:34:59,788
(DOOR CLOSES)

499
00:35:02,248 --> 00:35:03,666
(BELL TINKLING)

500
00:35:09,756 --> 00:35:10,799
Grandma!

501
00:35:11,549 --> 00:35:12,717
