514
00:35:45,291 --> 00:35:46,918
- (LAUGHING)
- (SCREAMING)

515
00:35:47,585 --> 00:35:49,212
- Don't be stupid!
- (LAUGHING)

516
00:35:50,463 --> 00:35:51,464
MAN: Come on!

517
00:35:51,548 --> 00:35:52,799
- Where is the money?
- (GRANDMA WONG GROANING)

518
00:35:55,969 --> 00:35:57,470
(GRUNTING)

519
00:36:05,019 --> 00:36:06,020
You!

520
00:36:06,104 --> 00:36:07,313
Why are you bothering an old lady?

