00:36:09,816 --> 00:36:11,276
- (SIZZLES)
- (MAN SCREAMS)

524
00:36:11,359 --> 00:36:12,652
(YELLING)

525
00:36:13,111 --> 00:36:14,112
(GRUNTS)

526
