766
00:53:20,472 --> 00:53:21,681
(WATER SPLASHES)

767
00:53:28,104 --> 00:53:29,397
Hey, I'm done.

768
00:53:30,440 --> 00:53:31,524
Hey.

769
00:53:31,608 --> 00:53:33,276
Wait for me outside.

770
00:53:35,153 --> 00:53:36,529
